Package: healthit.gov
Title: ONC Health IT (CHPL) Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for ONC Health IT data. Searches the Certified
    Health IT Product List (CHPL) API for certified EHR products and developers.
    Also provides access to static ONC CSV datasets on EHR adoption, prescribing,
    workforce, and policy. All functions return tibbles with typed columns.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr2, jsonlite, dplyr, tibble
